id": "44_1704765114.510357", "card_id": "Q_638690507", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "韩军宣布「韩朝之间不再存在缓冲区」，这意味着什么？会带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据韩联社 1 月 8 日报道，韩国联合参谋本部公报室室长李诚俊 8 日在记者会上表示，朝鲜共违反韩朝 2018 年签订的《九一九军事协议》3600 多次，并在西部海域连续三天实施炮击。李诚俊称，由此，敌对行为禁区（缓冲区）将不再存在。韩军宣布：韩朝之间不再存在缓冲区"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/638690507"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Izo/Mw7qQ6up+EAMaCTEwNDIwOTUzNSDuovKsBjAAOA5ALHIJNjM4NjkwNTA3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1704765114.511309", "card_id": "Q_637810847", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 18}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "目前各类 App 的评分机制存在哪些问题？如何优化，让真正好吃 / 好玩的店铺获得高评分？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "最近 #评分低的店可能更好吃# #年轻人报复性挤爆 3.5 分饭店# 等话题登上热搜引发不少网友共鸣 有网友在社交平台分享 自己曾经去过一些低分餐厅 味道却出乎意料 年轻人纷纷开始 寻找那些蒙尘的「明珠」"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/637810847"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Izo/Mw7qQ6up+EAMaCTEwNDAxNDExMyCMk9SsBjAAOBlALXIJNjM3ODEwODQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1704765114.512516", "card_id": "Q_634506440", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有点评类 App 存分数灌水情况，有餐厅靠赠菜等提高评价，年轻人挤爆 3.5 分饭店，如何看待此现象？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "「相信评分，不如相信自己的舌头。」据 Vista 看天下报道，近日，有关「评分低的店可能更好吃」的话题登上热搜，很多普通网友仿佛遇到知音一般，在评论区分享了自己在高分网红餐厅「踩雷」、爱吃的餐厅却只有 3.5 分的经历。一些年轻人在频频被花里胡哨的网红餐厅、真假难辨的探店视频「忽悠」之后，也开始叛逆地挥舞起「支持低分餐厅」的大旗，发现了不少明珠蒙尘的餐厅。 这一现象的大背景在于，一些点评类 App 存在分数灌水、好评率失真的情况。很多动辄 4.8 分往上、评论数高达成千上万条的餐厅，并不是靠美味征服食客，而是靠赠送菜品、提供优惠等「盘外招」刷出虚高评价。当有顾客因为这些店铺的高评分、高人气慕名而来，却发现其菜品、服务乏善可陈时，自然会失望而归，并对这类网红店铺产生警惕心。 年轻人报复性挤爆「3.5 分饭店」，高分餐厅不香了？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/634506440"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Izo/Mw7qQ6up+EAMaCTEwMzI4MDAwMyCI1eCrBjAAOBtALnIJNjM0NTA2NDQweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1704765114.513684", "card_id": "Q_636367595", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 80}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你的父母一日三餐都吃什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-708537334e66973fe0d7f15a63bd7902_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/636367595"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIzo/Mw7qQ6up+EAMaCTEwMzY5MzM4NiDM1ZusBjAAOI8BQC9yCTYzNjM2NzU5NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1704765114.514108", "card_id": "Q_634531777", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 51}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "敏感肌冬天用什么护肤品补水比较合适?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-539f5fcd0ae71dd8e657f765d7f8a373_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/634531777"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Izo/Mw7qQ6up+EAMaCTEwMzI4NTY1MyCni+GrBjAAOEpAMHIJNjM0NTMxNzc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1704765114.514500", "card_id": "Q_638538049", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 110}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": 